WAV file form

https://www.aelius.com/njh/wavemetatools/doc/riffmci.pdf
http://midi.teragonaudio.com/tech/wave.htm

<fmt-ck>
	"fmt " chunkID (ascii string)
	long chunkSize (in number of bytes)
	short wFormatTag (0x0001 for WAVE_FORMAT_PCM)
	short wChannels (number of channels)
	long dwSamplesPerSec 
	long dwAvgBytesPerSec
	short wBlockAlign (bytes per frame)
	short wBitsPerSample


https://fluidsynth.sourceforge.net/api/index.html